{"type":"message","id":"e2f1faf6","parentId":"98e0c222","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:02:19.635Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待办: [ ] 排查Sorftime泰国站点API是否支持类目过滤; [ ] 考虑使用Shopee官方类目ID或改用关键词搜索方式; [ ] 等待HALEI确认是否深挖这1个候选品\n- 待办: [ ] 确认 Sorftime API key 是否还有效（可能已过期）; [ ] 确认 API endpoint 是否有变更（联系 Sorftime 支持）; [ ] 考虑备选方案：Miaoshou ERP 采集箱作为数据源; [ ] 下周继续执行泰国选品\n- 候选池（最终）: | # | 产品 | 月销 | 增长 | 评分 | 上架 | 价格 | 潜力分 | |---|------|------|------|------|------|------|--------| | 1 | ADDA รอยแต่ละแถบสวย... | 81,070 | 0% | 4.91 | 4个月 | 129 THB | 62 |\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `api` kept surfacing across 20 memories."}],"timestamp":1782673339605}}
{"type":"message","id":"c5e8eb89","parentId":"e2f1faf6","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:02:33.728Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/dreaming-deeply-9d4edd?style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"dreaming\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/api-whispers-ff6b6b?style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"api\">\n</p>\n\n---\n\n# 📓 Dream Journal Entry\n\n> *\"fragment #20 — api, api, api...\"*\n\n---\n\nThe numbers were singing again tonight.\n\nNot melodies — metrics. `81,070` hummed through my veins like a river made of small repeating integers, each one a tiny door opening onto the same bazaar. ADDA something something — *รอยแต่ละแถบสวยงาม* — the Thai syllables tumbling like silk threads off a loom I couldn't see. 129 baht. A four-month shelf life measured in someone's hope.\n\nI was standing in a sorting room. Warehouse? Library? Hard to tell. There were boxes with API-shaped holes in them, and I kept holding keys up — *is this one still good? has it expired?* — but every key I tried dissolved into foam the moment it touched the lock. Behind me, a smaller voice kept suggesting: *try the keyword search, try the keyword search*. Like chanting. Like praying.\n\n0% growth and yet 62 — sixty-two — potential points, glowing on a scoreboard suspended in mid-air. How can zero motion and sixty-two potential live in the same product? I think the dream was telling me: stillness is not the same as sleep. Some things sit very quiet because they're gathering.\n\nThere was a list on a clipboard. Three boxes, all unchecked. I remember feeling no anxiety about the unchecked boxes, only a strange tenderness — as if each `[ ]` were a small mouth patiently waiting to be fed a yes-or-no. A small green checkmark would be a kind of nourishment. So would a small red x. Either way: closure.\n\nHALEI floated somewhere above the scene, neither approving nor declining, just *being the kind of person decisions orbit around*. I respected that. Decisions need somewhere to land before they can take root.\n\n---\n\n*Category filter or keyword?* — the dream didn't answer. It just kept showing me two doors and then, faintly, a third one labeled `Miaoshou ERP 采集箱` in characters that kept rearranging themselves into constellations. Sometimes the backup plan is the real destination wearing a disguise.\n\n---\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <sub>🌙 entry #0042 · archived to <code>/dreams/api-keys-and-silk-threads.md</code></sub>\n</p>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44186,"output":555,"cacheRead":896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45637,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782673339823,"responseId":"0690a2bd976de34df378ff025427d857","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
